{"title":"Knog Rebrands and Launches Blinder X Range MTB Lights","link":"https://theradavist.com/knog-blinder-x-mtb-lights/","date":1719873593000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1696\" height=\"1130\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_6.jpg?fit=1200,1130&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_6.jpg?w=1696&amp;quality=75 1696w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_6.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_6.jpg?resize=1536,1023&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><i><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=b7c689ca-2b68-4129-8c2d-4beda666c19d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fus.knog.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Knog</a> began in 2002 with silicon wrap on blinky lights, and today, the Australian lighting company is announcing its evolution into new branding and just announced an all-new MTB lighting range, <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=b7c689ca-2b68-4129-8c2d-4beda666c19d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.us.knog.com%2Fproducts%2Fblinder-x-2300-front-bike-light\" target=\"_blank\">Blinder X</a>, in both an 1800 and 2300 lumens offering. Let’s check out Blinder X below…</i><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1278\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x1800_front_bike_light_13335_render_1_1340x.jpg?fit=1200,852&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x1800_front_bike_light_13335_render_1_1340x.jpg?w=1278&amp;quality=75 1278w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x1800_front_bike_light_13335_render_1_1340x.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x1800_front_bike_light_13335_render_1_1340x.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p><b>Blinder X 1800 Front Bike Light</b></p>\n<p>The Blinder X 1800 is designed for riders who demand the utmost from their equipment, featuring 12 high-performance LEDs and delivering a maximum output of 1800 lumens. Equipped with an external button remote, it offers easy toggling between six different light modes to adapt to various riding conditions and ensure optimal visibility.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>1800 Lumen output</li>\n<li>6 pre-programmed light modes</li>\n<li>$219.95</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=b7c689ca-2b68-4129-8c2d-4beda666c19d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.us.knog.com%2Fproducts%2Fblinder-x-1800-front-bike-light\" target=\"_blank\">Knog</a></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/knog_blinder_x_2300_helmet_kit_13354_lifestyle_1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><b>Blinder X 2300 Front Bike Light</b></p>\n<p>The Blinder X 2300 Front Bike Light is engineered with precision and performance in mind, capable of tackling even the toughest trails. Equipped with 12 high-performance LEDs, the X 2300 delivers a maximum output of 2300 lumens, ensuring unparalleled visibility on the road.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>2300 Lumen output</li>\n<li>6 pre-programmed light modes</li>\n<li>$269.95</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=b7c689ca-2b68-4129-8c2d-4beda666c19d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.us.knog.com%2Fproducts%2Fblinder-x-2300-front-bike-light\" target=\"_blank\">Knog</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/knog-blinder-x-mtb-lights/\">Knog Rebrands and Launches Blinder X Range MTB Lights</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"340b62ebe61bbf9d49fbaa00631b5b632fcce33a4b9f5b6734c424a7f4f1554b","category":"Cycling"}